---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="News | Kreativ Sound"
  description="Latest sound releases and important updates from Kreativ Sound."
  canonical="https://kreativsound.com/news/"
  activeNav="news"
  ogImage="https://kreativsound.com/assets/thumbs/velvet-ruins.jpg"
>
  <section class="card page-main">
    <h1 class="page-title">News</h1>
    <p class="page-lead">Latest sound releases and important site updates.</p>
    <div class="stack news-stack">
      <article class="news-block">
        <h2>Latest Sound Releases</h2>
        <ul class="news-list">
          <li>
            <time datetime="2026-04-02">April 2, 2026</time>
            <span>Audio Alchemy Free is now live as a browser-based tool for generating three playable Vital preset variations from one short audio source.</span>
            <a href="/posts/audio-alchemy-free-launch-2026-04-02.html">Read launch note <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <time datetime="2026-03-21">March 21, 2026</time>
            <span>VELVET RUINS for Vital is now featured with a dark, worn-down preset collection built for cinematic melody and atmosphere.</span>
            <a href="/posts/velvet-ruins-release-2026-03-21.html">Read release note <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <time datetime="2026-03-03">March 3, 2026</time>
            <span>NEOLITH for Softube Models released with a focused analog-forward preset set for cinematic scoring.</span>
            <a href="/posts/neolith-release-2026-03-03.html">Read release note <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <time datetime="2026-02-26">February 26, 2026</time>
            <span>BIOFORMS for Synplant 2 was elevated as a core release with improved homepage placement.</span>
            <a href="/posts/bioforms-update-2026-02-26.html">Read update <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <time datetime="2026-02-25">February 25, 2026</time>
            <span>Catalog thumbnail pipeline was refreshed for faster loads and cleaner media management.</span>
            <a href="/posts/catalog-media-refresh-2026-02-25.html">Read update <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </article>
      <article class="news-block">
        <h2>Important Site News</h2>
        <ul class="news-list">
          <li>
            <time datetime="2026-04-04">April 4, 2026</time>
            <span>The public tool lineup now includes Audio Alchemy, Preset Mutator, and Wave Fracture under one Tools section.</span>
            <a href="/posts/tools-lineup-update-2026-04-04.html">Read update <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <time datetime="2026-03-06">March 6, 2026</time>
            <span>Navigation was refined with Font Awesome icons, a share button, and a new branded favicon system across the site.</span>
            <a href="/">See homepage refresh <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <time datetime="2026-03-06">March 6, 2026</time>
            <span>Top-level routes were cleaned up to use stable trailing-slash URLs for News, Learn, About, and Contact.</span>
            <a href="/about/">View updated navigation <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <time datetime="2026-03-05">March 5, 2026</time>
            <span>Learn section added with practical product articles for NEOLITH, BIOFORMS, and TECTONIC 2.</span>
            <a href="/learn/">Open Learn <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
